description:
The Genius is back at it again at the expense of his poor assistant.

In this issue he invents:

  • babysitting
  • 'live' tv
  • the baby bottle
  • the safe
  • trafficlights
  • group travel
  • the helicopter
  • a deck of cards and subsequently poker and bridge
  • Santa Claus
  • land speed world records
  • fishing
  • speeding tickets
  • the alarm clock
  • weather reports
  • Basile invents origami
  • the ice-pick
